==================
Starlette APISpec
==================

    Easy APISpec integration for Starlette

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/Woile/starlette-apispec.svg?style=flat-square
    :alt: Travis
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/Woile/starlette-apispec

